00:38:57.110 --> 00:38:58.630
Bagaimana jika salah seorang daripada kita cedera?

00:38:58.630 --> 00:38:59.430
Betul, betul.

00:38:59.670 --> 00:39:01.530
Doktor Keajaiban Fei adalah penting.

00:39:01.880 --> 00:39:03.280
Ketua Pentadbir Anda.

